"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-03-14-Olympics-Paris-mayor-tells-air-conditioning-fans-to-trust-science--1rY7fnfO5lm-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  With competing nations split over whether to enter into the spirit of the \\\"Green Games\\\" or throw money at success, whatever the environmental cost, Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo told those nations planning on installing air conditioning at the athletes' village to \\\"trust the science\\\" instead.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Temperatures are expected to soar again in the European summer after setting records in 2023, but there will be no air conditioning in the athletes' rooms at Paris 2024, which has pledged to host the \\\"greenest ever\\\" Games.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, buildings in the athletes' village have been designed with a cooling system drawing water from underground and facades orientated so they get little direct sun.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This village was designed to avoid the need for air conditioning, even in very, very high temperatures, in order to maintain comfortable temperatures,\\\" Hidalgo told Reuters on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999974571033408, \"rank\": 2.54290296923881e-06, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas Bach (L), president of the International Olympic Committee, visits the Paris 2024 Olympic Village construction site in Paris, France, December 1, 2023.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1780697293344318e-19, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995946896750402, \"rank\": 0.0002022874671797372, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  With climate scientists warning that global warming has produced more extreme weather patterns in much of the world, organizers of Paris 2024 have said they want to halve the carbon footprint compared with the Rio 2016 and London 2012 Summer Games.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we have to trust science on two counts.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first is what scientists are telling us about the fact that we are on the brink of a precipice.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone, including the athletes, must be aware of this,\\\" said Hidalgo.\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9997171859671096, \"rank\": 0.0002828940394572381, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And secondly, we have to trust the scientists when they help us to construct buildings in a sober way that allows us to make do without air conditioning.\\\"\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France's President Emmanuel Macron (2nd L) visits the Paris 2024 Olympic Village in Paris, France, February 29, 2024.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1887, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995946896750402, \"rank\": 0.0002022874671797372, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1906, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1941, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1780697293344318e-19, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1978, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995946896750402, \"rank\": 0.0002022874671797372, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Not all competitors are convinced  The Olympic Committees from Australia, Brazil, Canada and Norway are among those who believe it will not be enough.\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999773247688336, \"rank\": 2.263926668393174e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2085, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9999987724362004, \"rank\": 9.049687816512261e-07, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 2093, \"end\": 2099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999991646291, \"rank\": 5.671332232089038e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9999969825116801, \"rank\": 2.291172604229392e-06, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our clear wish is that there should be air conditioning in all rooms,\\\" the Norwegian Committee told Reuters, with Brazil saying \\\"the heat forecast\\\" made it \\\"necessary to invest in renting air conditioning units for the entire delegation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2239, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9982662287453271, \"rank\": 0.0016435802171209373, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999974571033408, \"rank\": 2.54290296923881e-06, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 2278, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9999987724362004, \"rank\": 9.049687816512261e-07, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's Chef de Mission Anna Meares said they were \\\"looking at portable air conditioners to offer the athletes should they choose to if it gets hot, if it's uncomfortable.\\\"\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999773247688336, \"rank\": 2.263926668393174e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2416, \"end\": 2431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chef de Mission\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\"}, {\"begin\": 2432, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadian Olympic Committee told Reuters it had \\\"implemented a number of heat mitigation strategies in Paris to complement the measures put in place by the Paris 2024 Organizing Committee, including air conditioning units in some athlete rooms in case of extreme heat.\\\"\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2586, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999974571033408, \"rank\": 2.54290296923881e-06, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 2688, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2741, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A view of a bedroom inside one of the athletes' apartments at the Paris 2024 Olympic Village in Paris, France, February 26, 2024.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2922, \"end\": 2932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2933, \"end\": 2948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1780697293344318e-19, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 2952, \"end\": 2957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2959, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995946896750402, \"rank\": 0.0002022874671797372, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  What matters for Hidalgo, however, is that the athletes' village, which will be home to some 6,000 Parisiens after the Games, is a sustainable project.\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3009, \"end\": 3016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9997171859671096, \"rank\": 0.0002828940394572381, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But then they do what they want; I am not going to tell them what to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What matters to me is that these buildings, these flats will become a neighborhood where people from L'Ile-Saint-Denis, Saint-Ouen and Saint-Denis (in the Paris suburbs) will live.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3387, \"end\": 3392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These new buildings will not need air conditioning, so we are working for the long term.\\\"\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lending support to the organizers' vision, several other delegations have said they fully trust they will not need air conditioning at the Games.\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have visited the Olympic Village in Paris regularly in the last years and rate the clever cooling system installed in floor and ceiling to be sufficient for the climate zone,\\\" the German Olympic Committee told Reuters.\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3672, \"end\": 3687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1780697293344318e-19, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 3691, \"end\": 3696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3835, \"end\": 3859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Olympic_Sports_Confederation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"German Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Olympic_Sports_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Olympic_Sports_Confederation\"}, {\"begin\": 3865, \"end\": 3872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999974571033408, \"rank\": 2.54290296923881e-06, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Additional passive prevention coming with the windows does further add to this.\", \"from\": 3875, \"to\": 3955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, we have asked our federations whether or not they want to rent the extra air conditioning offered by the Paris 2024 rate card system.\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 4103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4075, \"end\": 4085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vast majority of our federations have judged this to be unnecessary.\\\"\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4439, \"entities\": []}]}"